{"tid":1093926,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯成英超Big6唯一虧蝕球會　最衰係佢","createTime":"2019-04-06T02:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T03:39:17.000Z","uid":4661,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d994bdf88b775095d4aa5b98753e377c03a446","tid":1093926,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:15:58.000Z","msg":"曼聯近期續約唔順利，主要原因係球員本身人工太高，但續約時仲要求加薪，令球隊陷入困局，美聯社為英超Big6於2017至18球季進行數據比較，發現6大球會中只有曼聯出現虧蝕，死因正正係薪酬支出過高。 <br />\n<br />\n曼聯係6間球會中收入最高，共有5.9億鎊，但人工支出亦高達2.96億鎊，結果在盈利一欄出現負數，錄得3730萬鎊虧蝕，成績唔合格。 <br />\n<br />\n出現如此局面，只怪曼聯球員薪酬政策失衡，最離譜首推廢鋒阿歷斯山齊士，周薪達到50萬鎊，亦因為佢嘅存在，搞到保羅普巴、迪基亞等主力，個個喊加人工，令曼聯虧蝕情況無法改善。 <br />\n<br />\n講到賺錢最多嘅球會，就係熱刺，雖然佢哋收入最低，只有3.81億鎊，但由於人工支出亦最低，只有1.48億鎊，故錄得1.13億鎊盈利，成績非常理想。 <br />\n<br />\n球會　 收入　 盈利　 薪酬支出 <br />\n曼城 5.01億鎊 1040萬鎊 2.6億鎊 <br />\n利物浦 4.55億鎊 1.06億鎊 2.63億鎊 <br />\n熱刺 3.81億鎊 1.13億鎊 1.48億鎊 <br />\n阿仙奴 4.04億鎊 5660萬鎊 2.4億鎊 <br />\n車路士 4.43億鎊 6200萬鎊 2.44億鎊<br />\n曼聯 5.9億鎊 -3730萬鎊 2.96億鎊 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190406/photo/bkn-20190406031914535-0406_00882_001_03p.jpg?20190406040330\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190406%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190406031914535-0406_00882_001_03p.jpg%3F20190406040330&h=a0ab9671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2-prod.mirror.co.uk/incoming/article11897001.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/sanchez-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.mirror.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle11897001.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615b%2Fsanchez-2.jpg&h=46239768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh%2Fsource.gif&h=f11c7f5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3439a772e9fc119d6a3c01f360b8b707f2aa5c0","tid":1093926,"uid":120821,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"曼城點解有咁多收入？<br />\n金主科水渣下？"},{"pid":"79ae8cf458a0b9da8a8ed6493c8ff0d906c8a38c","tid":1093926,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"美聯社都信山齊士50萬週薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace208807f1423bfb7a05df474e1a962f647415f","tid":1093926,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b3439a772e9fc119d6a3c01f360b8b707f2aa5c0","tid":1093926,"uid":120821,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"曼城點解有咁多收入？<br />\n金主科水渣下？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:22:03.000Z","msg":"自己贊助自己"},{"pid":"2441552758e429a0325c386de04d079494c3e430","tid":1093926,"uid":84228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"2019都仲有人信50萬周薪"},{"pid":"38e8fcb453f81bd20365a8d9aab8e9777fa679a0","tid":1093926,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b3439a772e9fc119d6a3c01f360b8b707f2aa5c0","tid":1093926,"uid":120821,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"曼城點解有咁多收入？<br />\n金主科水渣下？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"心口贊助商伊蒂哈德航空一季比200m曼城洗"},{"pid":"229706ec9a274f04dec6835feb3cb3161c8a303b","tid":1093926,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"賤種朗筆錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622dcd721599f42a66159fceace49ec0bdf131f5","tid":1093926,"uid":1147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"